  "businessLogic": [
    "Determine the feature type from SlotsDTO.",
    "For 'FundTransfer': retrieve TransferDTO from SlotsDTO, iterate over each TxnLineDTO leg, look up DepositAccountEntity by account number via repository, build a TransferLegContext per leg, store all leg contexts in SlotsDTO, and set purposeId/customerId/accountId from the DEBIT leg.",
    "For 'MultiCreditTransaction': retrieve MultiCreditTransactionDTO, iterate over each TxnLineDTO leg with indicator 'CREDIT', look up DepositAccountEntity per leg, build TransferLegContext entries, and store all leg contexts in SlotsDTO.",
