    "For 'TDAccountPreClosure': retrieve TDAccountPreClosureDTO from SlotsDTO and extract accountNumber.",
    "For AccountClosure/TDAccountPreClosure: look up DepositAccountEntity by accountNumber via repository; if found, set accountCurrency, purposeId, customerId, and accountId in SlotsDTO; if not found, throw FbpValidationException with ACCOUNT_IS_INVALID error code."
